    <item>
      <title>Ledger 首席执行官：“如果不是自我托管，那为什么要使用加密货币？”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-11/ledger-ceo-if-not-self-custody-why-crypto-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Ledger 首席执行官 Ian Rogers 讨论了自托管加密钱包的使用案例，并表示人工智能和区块链“齐头并进”。他在“Bloomberg Crypto”节目中与 Tim Stenovec 和 Sonali Basak 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-11/ledger-ceo-if-not-self-custody-why-crypto-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 18:48:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特鲁多的竞争对手反对提高资本利得税，承诺实施新的减税措施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/trudeau-s-rival-opposes-capital-gains-hike-promises-new-tax-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大保守党领袖皮埃尔·波利耶夫 (Pierre Poilievre) 表示，他将投票反对政府提高资本利得税纳入税率的提议，结束了数周以来人们对他在此问题上立场的猜测。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/trudeau-s-rival-opposes-capital-gains-hike-promises-new-tax-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 18:44:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管面临重大风险，国债拍卖仍吸引强劲需求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/treasury-auction-draws-strong-demand-despite-key-risks-ahead</link>
      <description><![CDATA[债券价格上涨，抹去了上周强劲的就业数据造成的部分损失，尽管周三接近潜在的不稳定事件，但 10 年期国债拍卖仍吸引了异常强劲的需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/treasury-auction-draws-strong-demand-despite-key-risks-ahead</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 18:22:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国央行下调经济增长预期，因预算削减预期加剧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/bank-of-france-cuts-growth-outlook-as-budget-cuts-seen-biting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国央行下调了未来两年的经济增速预测，因为该预测考虑了能源价格上涨以及为消除预算赤字而削减开支所导致的经济活动受到打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/bank-of-france-cuts-growth-outlook-as-budget-cuts-seen-biting</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 18:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>银行领导称房地产市场困境仍局限于写字楼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/bank-leaders-say-real-estate-pain-is-still-confined-to-office</link>
      <description><![CDATA[富国银行和 PNC 金融服务集团的高管表示，大多数行业的商业房地产风险仍在可控范围内，但办公楼风险仍将困扰贷方。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/bank-leaders-say-real-estate-pain-is-still-confined-to-office</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 17:56:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯托尔滕贝格谈北约对乌克兰的长期承诺</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-11/stoltenberg-on-nato-s-long-term-commitment-to-ukraine-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[北约秘书长延斯·斯托尔滕贝格表示，对乌克兰的长期支持承诺将带来更多的可预测性和责任感。斯托尔滕贝格将于周三访问布达佩斯期间与匈牙利总理维克托·奥尔班举行会谈。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-11/stoltenberg-on-nato-s-long-term-commitment-to-ukraine-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 17:54:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>穆迪将联合地产评级降至垃圾级，因写字楼空置率过高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/allied-properties-cut-to-junk-by-moody-s-on-office-vacancy-woes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[穆迪评级周二将联合地产房地产公司的评级下调至垃圾级，理由是这家加拿大写字楼业主的债务水平高，而且入住率下降将影响其履行义务的能力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/allied-properties-cut-to-junk-by-moody-s-on-office-vacancy-woes</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 17:44:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>财政风险扭曲巴西掉期利率上涨预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/fiscal-risks-distort-brazilian-swaps-to-price-in-rate-hikes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[人们对巴西控制财政赤字能力的怀疑日益增加，引发了投资状况的突然变化，扭曲了巴西的掉期利率市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/fiscal-risks-distort-brazilian-swaps-to-price-in-rate-hikes</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 17:41:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高利率令美国货币基金不再担忧改革</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/us-money-funds-look-past-reform-angst-thanks-to-still-high-rates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国货币市场基金行业仍在享受长期高利率的推动，摆脱了今年晚些时候生效的改革带来的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/us-money-funds-look-past-reform-angst-thanks-to-still-high-rates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 14:47:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股市上涨，因稳健的国债销售刺激 CPI 押注：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[此前，美国政府成功售出 390 亿美元国债，引发外界猜测周三公布的通胀数据将有助于美联储今年降息。随后，股市跟随债市上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 22:14:15 GMT</pubDate>
